{"tid":1121503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"21歲港鐵學徒大圍站墮軌　遭列車輾斃","createTime":"2019-04-23T10:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T12:29:24.000Z","uid":20933,"like":83,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"41968034e38eeb58ca05d29ab570c8cdcd27de08","tid":1121503,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190423/large/1555990594_b06b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190423%2Flarge%2F1555990594_b06b.jpg&h=fd42791f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周一（22日）晚上10時許，一名男子於港鐵東鐵綫大圍站墮軌，慘遭列車輾過並捲入車底，消防接報到場將他他救出，證實他已明顯死亡。受事件影響，九龍塘站往返沙田站的列車服務一度受阻，港鐵一度派出免費接駁巴士來往九龍塘站和沙田站，接載受影響乘客。至晚上11時45分，東鐵綫事故已經處理好，列車服務陸續回復正常。<br />\n<br />\n死者姓彭21歲，懷疑因為生活問題不開心跳軌輕生，警方進行調查後，認為案件並無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵發言人表示，昨晚一名港鐵學徒於大圍站不幸離世，港鐵對此表示難過，並已聯絡及慰問其家屬，提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OGWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=f198d5dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"2a7764caaed518f034f6123deabde8287c9cf1f5","tid":1121503,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:58:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190423/59517902\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190423%2F59517902&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OGWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=134e6fa4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190423%2F59517902&h=9d462339\" data-auto-link t